{"tid":980983,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"舞台劇演員會用咩方法記對白","createTime":"2019-01-14T01:48:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T02:51:48.000Z","uid":228995,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a5e2ba811c4250c4dc044671df8777f7f00a220f","tid":980983,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T01:48:14.000Z","msg":"雖然每次演出都會排戲<br />\n每次睇舞台劇都覺得演員好厲害<br />\n拍電影拍電視劇都可以NG<br />\n但舞台劇最少都一個幾鐘<br />\n一個演員要由頭到尾背熟對白<br />\n仲要配合演技，同其他演員互動<br />\n<br />\n究竟舞台劇演員一般會用咩方法記到咁長對白？<br />\n有無行内人可以分享下舞台劇演員有無任何同一般人唔同嘅記憶法？<br />\n<br />\n利申：平時記憶力好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb317a8e9c158058fa99b325c2cb0403a345e8f","tid":980983,"uid":112901,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T01:50:50.000Z","msg":"大腦記憶法"},{"pid":"a348177866972507050a00b8757ad4d30b42bee0","tid":980983,"uid":62822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T02:42:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9c4653cf781e2613e9d6b53fdec259a80888ca94","tid":980983,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a348177866972507050a00b8757ad4d30b42bee0","tid":980983,"uid":62822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T02:42:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T02:51:48.000Z","msg":"上星期睇完短暫的婚姻<br />\n現場出面馬上有劇本賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係發現演員有唔記得對白<br />\n不過都記得90%"}]}